ğŸªœ Step 4: Style Table (Optional for Now)

You can add this CSS to your existing style.css file to make the results table look better:

table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

th, td {
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  padding: 10px;
  text-align: left;
}

th {
  background-color: #007bff;
  color: white;
}

tr:nth-child(even) {
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
}

